            resetMenuAt,
            fortuneSheetTabMenuItems.indexOf(fortuneSheetTabColorCommand),
          ).center,
    );
    await tester.pump();
    await tester.tapAt(
      topLeft +
          Offset(
            fortuneSheetTabColorMenuRect(resetMenuAt).left + 20,
